Package: P2C2M2
Type: Package
Title: Posterior Predictive Checks of Coalescent Models
Version: 0.02
Date: 2025-01-15
Author: Arley Camargo, Joaquin Villamil
Maintainer: Arley Camargo <arley.camargo@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
